# MedBook / NeuroFax — recommended host crontab.
# Install with: `crontab ops/crontab.example` (on the deploy host, as the
# user that owns the repo checkout).
#
# The docker-compose `certbot` sidecar handles renewal, so we only need
# the nightly database backup here.

MAILTO=""

# Nightly Postgres backup → MinIO, 03:00 UTC.
0 3 * * * cd /opt/medbook && ./ops/backup.sh >> /var/log/medbook-backup.log 2>&1
